divs: Sighting DetailsI was heading to greene county at Lexington rd at 6:20am as I was driving under a green light I caught 5 long light fly a straigt in the sky over my car and I could tell it had no noise and was not a plane or helicopter of any type! it was fast and caught my eye because I have never witnessed anything like this before! as it flew over me it eventually disappeared over the tree line! I was in awe that I just encounterd a ufo! it eas long rectangle lights in a straight path and was multi-collard ad it was huge something that low you should off heard a noise but nothing was heard! very weird to say the most!
